Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:09.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}地下城在怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:14.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怨恨我们将他们禁足在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:17.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}乌拉斯 人都怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对这件事 我并未有所耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:49.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}果然是阶层主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:05.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:43.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:42.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}要尽快去救他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:43.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你真的打算去救他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就凭我们这个团队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:03.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}去救他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:07.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}身为领队的你虽然失职
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:11.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但是 并没有做错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}千草小姐 神明大人拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}各位 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:20.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:28.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}大家千万别勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:36.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:40.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}劳尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:53.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为什么…为什么事情会演变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你会妨碍贝尔大人战斗 所以搬走你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:14.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}记得要感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}感谢我们家的那个好好先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:29.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那是什么玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:31.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}波路斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:36.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}召集所有能用的武器和冒险者 去征讨阶层主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别开玩笑了 安朵美达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那不是普通的阶层主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:43.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们…已经没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:48.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}事实上我们已经无法自行离开这一层
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:53.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}若不击败阶层主 我们应该无法离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:56.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:01.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}小子们 齐心协力干掉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}把城内的人全部给我找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}胆敢说半句丧气话的胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:10.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}永远禁止他踏入我们的城内半步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:12.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}给他们见识一下冒险者的骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}快点离开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:41.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}无形鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:57.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:02.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}果然与普通的阶层主的实力不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}潜力能力眼看达到Lv5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}疾风 援军来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}现在四周的魔导士将要开始咏唱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你继续吸引Goraiasu的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:19.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:24.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}让我和你一同分散敌人的注意力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}好 小子们听着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}安朵美达会替我们做饵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:34.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}毫无顾虑 尽情咏唱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}让他吃我们一招厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:42.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}波路斯 你给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}发射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}尽量多争取点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:54.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}咏唱一旦结束…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:08.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}果然名不虚传
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:10.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}武器要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}坏了就换
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}凑活着一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:17.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别想团队合作了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}只要别妨碍到别人就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}用自己的方式战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:39.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:42.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:58.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}好 大家准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}让他尝尝我们的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}发射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}给他致命一击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:40.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}自我再生…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:48.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}克朗尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}琉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:51.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}克朗尼先生负责对付四周的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们负责拖住Goraiasu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不能这样一直被压着打
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:03.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}只要争取到时间 还有战斗力的魔导士们能再次使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}即便如此仍无法消灭他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:09.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}直到再次击败他 无论几次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:10.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}琉小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:11.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:25.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}赫斯缇雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}支援者 你没事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请设法收集一切能使用的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:32.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}听见了吗 麻烦你回城里去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:33.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:35.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}千草大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}听见刚才一声爆炸 飞奔出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}应该赶去樱花他们身边去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:43.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:50.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}疾风 你这样做是送死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我也必须做到与之相应的付出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:05.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就算想对付魔石 阶层主的身体太坚硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不过即便如此 迟早还是会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}如果有效的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}千草 拿我的盾牌来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不行 你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}樱花会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}拜托你了 千草
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:41.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我不想做一个动口不动手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:46.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}牺牲他人的同时 自己却无法挺身而出的讨厌家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:49.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:06.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}克朗尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:08.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}疾风 我们闪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:21.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰闪电
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:55.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:06.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可恶 混账
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:10.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}樱花大人 樱花大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:12.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}樱花…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:15.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}克朗尼先生 快回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:21.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:22.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:26.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}还有呼吸 但伤口很深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:29.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}疾风 这里拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:34.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}千草大人 之后麻烦你照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}去吧 精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:41.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就算仅能争取一点时间也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:47.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔一定醒过来 重新站起来去打败那个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}女神赫斯缇雅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:54.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你应该也看到了 贝尔他可以做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:57.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔能击败那个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:09.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 快睁开眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:10.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 贝尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:11.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}大家都在奋力作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}即便面对如此可怕的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:22.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们只能寄希望于你帮助大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}站起来 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:27.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:31.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:39.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但我的身体无论如何 根本无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:43.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}动起来 动起来 动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我必须要去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:49.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为了神明大人 为了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:54.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}若拥有被称做英雄的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:56.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不是手持刀剑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}并非手持盾牌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:02.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}更不是给予治疗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:07.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}能赌上自己性命的人 才有资格被称为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:12.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}保护同伴 拯救心爱女人 赌上自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:16.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}无所谓气馁 不怕跌倒 放声大哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:20.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}胜利者始终存在于失败者中间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:22.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}梦想成真
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}高呼理想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:33.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这样一来 你就能成为最威武的男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不能让她为我感到羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:50.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为了拯救无比重要的同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:52.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:56.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:15:58.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}让憧憬燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}让愿望怒吼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:29.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}界限解除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别让他们跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:49.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}远处浩瀚无垠的森林天空 镶嵌于无穹夜空的无限星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}愚笨的我用声音回应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请降临星火之庇佑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:52.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10\pos(640,53)}此等高速战斗中居然咏唱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:57.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请将光之慈悲赐予抛弃汝之人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:56.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10\pos(640,53)}太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我主神明请屈尊听愿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:06.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}打破世间万物的吾之武神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:08.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}遵从上天的引导
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请将御身巍然的神力赐予卑微渺小的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:16.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我知道 明明是我把你抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但我还有想拯救的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:23.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}拜托了 让我将你粉碎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:27.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}漂泊的风 流浪的旅人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:29.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}翱翔天空 穿越荒野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}以寄宿星屑的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}看来我也必须拿出真本事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:48.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}讨伐敌人 星光之风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:48.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10\fs26\pos(725,665)}Lumina Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:00.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}由上天下凡 统帅下界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:02.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神武斗征
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}布都御魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这是重力结界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}压不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:37.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你们都让开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火月！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那是…格罗索的魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:50.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}超越原有的那把
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:57.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不要将固执和同伴放在天平的两端衡量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:00.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的 这只不过是我的固执
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:04.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}面对落差极大的压倒性劣势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:28.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}仅凭孤军作战的微弱反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:35.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}也就是所谓的英雄一击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:59.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}连那一击都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:01.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我的贝尔·克朗尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:11.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}更快 更强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}能飞跃地更高
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:51.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人 贝尔大人成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:20:59.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:05.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}干得漂亮 未完少年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:11.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我荷米斯确实亲眼见证
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:16.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}毫无潜质?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:17.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}宙斯你胡说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你孙子毫无疑问是货真价实的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:25.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}他是你眷族留下的最后一位英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:28.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}时代正在向前推进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:30.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我绝对要用这双眼睛见证
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:32.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:34.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}发生在这片名为欧拉丽的大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}即将被载入史册的历史大事件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:40.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}英雄们的成长 以及其生与死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:45.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为神所爱的他们会携手叙写眷族的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}眷族神话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:42.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:26.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10\pos(648,657)}相当厉害的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:29.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}{\blur10\pos(648,657)}不准喝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:32.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}{\blur10\pos(648,657)}还发生过这样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:36.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}{\blur10\pos(648,657)}都在喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.98,0:22:40.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}{\blur10\pos(648,657)}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:38.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你辛苦了 贝尔
